Quickstrike:

 

 

Quickstrike saw two of the Dinobots barge into the ship. He eyed their path and ran after them. "They got in th' base!" he yelled out.  He ran fast as he could after them. He went after them until he found them at the door of the bridge. The bottom of his feet spat sparks and he came to a violent halt. He aimed at one of them who was Stegotron (Hope I got that right.) and fired at his turned back.
